Protocol  : TLSv1.3
Cipher    : TLS_AES_256_GCM_SHA384
Meaning:
TLS version negotiation succeeded
Cipher suite agreement succeeded
Key exchange completed
If handshake failed, these fields are missing.
2️⃣ Certificate Chain Is Returned
Example:
复制代码

Certificate chain
 0 s:CN=example.com
   i:CN=R3,O=Let's Encrypt
Meaning:
Server sent its certificate
Intermediate CA(s) provided
Handshake reached certificate stage
No certificate block → handshake did not complete.
3️⃣ Verify Return Code
Most important line:
复制代码

Verify return code: 0 (ok)
Meaning:
Certificate chain validated
Trusted by your local CA bundle
No signature/path errors
Non-zero codes indicate trust or chain problems — TLS may still be established but not trusted.
4️⃣ SSL-Session Block Present
Example:
